    • toFileOutput

      org.eclipse.collections.api.collection.ImmutableCollection<String[]> toFileOutput()
      Return a list with String arrays as entries. The entries should have the format to first state the type of inconsistency, then the sentence number and third the id of the model element or the name of the text element (or both). Fourth entry can be an optional confidence value
      Returns:
      List with String arrays as entry with the format {SentenceNumber, ModelElementId/TextElement, (optional) confidence}.
